{"tid":1553072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我報案 (張錦良 48328)話唔知會唔會有trap喎 點算好","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:01:33.000Z","uid":168668,"like":166,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"6e856ad288f5734503f82ae7e162a1d14771ce8f","tid":1553072,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"話說2019年9月8號夜晚8點左右<br />\n我見屋企樓下有好多違例泊車<br />\n因為我屋企附近好多老人院<br />\n我怕d呀sir老豆老母係上面住<br />\n有咩事白車入唔到去<br />\n佢地老豆老母因為救唔切死左就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我咪盡好市民責任打去999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知經999轉介後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 48328 張錦良 沙展 </span></strong>就cut左我三次線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好死唔死<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">48328 張錦良 沙展 </span></strong>第三次cut線又冇禁好個制<br />\n比我聽到呢句野&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-922435328-720309122/trap-48328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-922435328-720309122%2Ftrap-48328&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=02dd803d\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-922435328-720309122/trap-48328</a> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留意1:02</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a3fda1bc786ba9024cdd87cf54e2bda61196bea7","tid":1553072,"uid":168668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b64bd891bd7db538b60c495848247f3ea3e99b1","tid":1553072,"uid":168668,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"好驚警察叔叔d爸爸媽媽有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa